","msg":"我估個原理好似你敷mask咁掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:41:49.000Z","msg":"我幾年前用過 白咗好多<br />\n當然唔好期望用完即白<br />\n佢係唔覺唔覺咁白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一日你望返自己依家嘅相<br />\n同返幾年前幾比<br />\n會有好大分別<br />\n到依家無用幾年 仲成日飲茶<br />\n已經黃返好多<br />\n但仲會keep住有人問點解啲牙咁白<br />\n我覺得好work<br />\n不過如果日日痴真係會痛<br />\n同埋我啲牙唔係好大粒<br />\n痴到牙肉都好&rsquo;嗱&rsquo;<br />\n所以我會剪走少少先<br />\n我覺得可以買一盒試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f8d12c34e686dc3b7b879677b2734acbf5e46e","tid":772251,"uid":27509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"個牙貼我有用過真係會白<br />\n但棚牙真係變到好酸<br />\n酸到坐立不安做乜都無心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1691c18ba261de50f7787712da4fa4aaa2b840b","tid":772251,"uid":82779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"有冇d唔傷牙既美白牙齒方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071bc3c419d915be218c664f93bca2f8e2b447a6","tid":772251,"uid":71284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"804a21688c2a896ba2ad5d39e2ae5a99aa280307","tid":772251,"uid":60291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c5f4f9203ba8fd8c6f178fc689ab8c780eb5ccc","tid":772251,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2397203347c49fc9b804230ee751210eac6d34fb","tid":772251,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"用個排會敏感 過一排先無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"就係聽人講會敏感所以我唔敢貼太近牙肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩我冇事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T15:31:48.000Z","msg":"要用幾耐到先會有明顯少少既效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"特登login答<br />\n我自己啲牙以前好黃<br />\n聽完個fd推介（佢排牙無啦啦勁白 加上佢果排曬黑左 真係望落好似啲黑人咁排牙勁白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我就去左萬寧買<br />\n用左頭三日早晚一次 即刻有分別<br />\n第四日開始就每日一次<br />\n佢包裝好似話想快啲有效果就早晚用<br />\n不過我都驚有敏感牙齒所以淨係頭三日係早晚用<br />\n一盒好似廿塊我用淨左7塊就冇再用過因爲啲牙勁白<br />\n之後仲推介左比超過5個frd用<br />\n但佢地有3個話啲牙真係敏感左<br />\n所以巴打自己衡量下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}